{"title":"Affordable 8bar Mitte v3 all-road bike transforms, gravel to road faster than ever!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/26/affordable-8bar-mitte-v3-all-road-bike-transforms-gravel-to-road-faster-than-ever/","date":1622034978000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>8bar’s versatile alloy Mitte v3 has just simplified its transition from road to gravel, then back again thanks to a unique set of dropout flip chips. Now all you need is two dedicated wheelsets to go from everyday road riding on 28mm tires to weekend gravel exploring on 45mm knobbies, with just about a minute with a multi-tool to swap from one mode to the next…</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" data-ezsrc=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/475833524\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p><p>Developed in Berlin, the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=8bar+mitte\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mitte</a> has been one of the most adaptable &amp; affordable road, all-road, cross, gravel, and bikepacking bikes since <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2016/03/17/8bar-bikes-goes-truly-road-mitte-convertible-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">it came onto the scene</a> five years ago. While that initially involved interchangeable forks, sliding dropouts, and a lot of adjustment going back-and-forth. Now it’s as simple as turning around a set of flip chips at each axle.</p><h3>2in1 Twist thru-axle flip chips &amp; adjustable geometry</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip.jpg\" alt=\"8bar Mitte v3 alloy all-road bike, affordable adjustable 2in1 road and gravel bike,&nbsp;Twist flip chip\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090736/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 