2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_thru-axle-flip-chip-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The simple, <em>why-didn’t-I-think-of-that</em> 8bar secret is their new Twist thru-axle flip chips. The 2-position adjustable alloy inserts at both the front &amp; rear thru-axles move each wheel 10mm towards your brake pad, meaning once you flip them around you don’t even need to adjust your brakes.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip.jpg\" alt=\"8bar Mitte v3 alloy all-road bike, affordable adjustable 2in1 road and gravel bike,&nbsp;flip chip\" width=\"1400\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-297x170.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-800x457.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-768x439.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-696x398.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-1068x610.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-735x420.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-297x170.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-800x457.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-768x439.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-696x398.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-1068x610.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090729/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_Twist-flipchip-735x420.jpg 735w\"></a></p><p>You just have one set of wheels for road riding with road tires, a cassette &amp; 140mm rotors, and a separate gravel set for off-road riding with up to 45mm tires, the same cassette &amp; 160mm rotors. Swap back &amp; forth as quick as you can unthread two axles, flip the Twist inserts around, and pop in the second set of wheels.</p><figure id=\"attachment_260014\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-260014\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090723/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090723/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"8bar Mitte v3 alloy all-road bike, affordable adjustable 2in1 road and gravel bike,&nbsp;geometry\" width=\"1800\" height=\"700\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090723/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_geometry.jpg 1800w,