e><p>Instant shorter chainstays &amp; wheelbase, lower stack, lower center of gravity, and 1/2 degree steeper head &amp; seat angles when going from gravel to road modes.</p><p>No other adjustments needed.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete.jpg\" alt=\"8bar Mitte v3 alloy all-road bike, affordable adjustable 2in1 road and gravel bike,&nbsp;bikepacking\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090716/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_bikepacking-complete-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Beyond the easy-to-use new flip chips. The 2in1 Mitte v3 keeps most of the same features that made the original versatile. 8bar’s classic triple-butted 6061 aluminum tubing keeps the frame reasonably light at a claimed 1700g, responsive, and affordable. The new bike features a tapered headtube &amp; internal headset for a 1.5″ tapered steerer, a PF30 bottom bracket, 27.2mm seatpost, flat mount disc brakes, and 12mm thru-axles. It gets internal cable routing in the main triangle, dropped seatstays for a bit more comfort, and three sets of water bottle bosses (3-pack on the toptube, plus a pair below). The frame also offers fender mounts, although only the dedicated gravel fork has its own fender tabs.</p><figure id=\"attachment_260012\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-260012\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road.jpg\" alt=\"8bar Mitte v3 alloy all-road bike, affordable adjustable 2in1 road and gravel bike,&nbsp;fork options\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road.jpg 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-297x165.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-800x444.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-768x427.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-1536x853.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-696x387.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-1068x593.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-756x420.jpg 756w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road.jpg 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-297x165.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-800x444.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-768x427.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-1536x853.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-696x387.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-1068x593.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090710/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_fork-options-2in1-Gravel-Road-756x420.jpg 756w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-260012\">8bar Mitte v3 carbon fork options (left-right): 2in1 adjustable, Gravel fixed, Road fixed</figcaption></figure><p>8bar offers three full carbon fork options depending on what you want to do with your Mitte. The 500g 2in1 fork is the most versatile &amp; most expensive with the Twist flip chips to swap geometry back &amp; forth, but no extra mounts. The regular fixed axle Gravel fork weighs the same, costs less, and adds fender tabs and a pair of cage bosses on each leg.&nbsp; The regular fixed Road fork has a slimmer, tapered leg design that weighs less with the shorter axle-to-crown length &amp; no extra bosses, and costs the same as the fixed Gravel fork.</p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>Pick the 2in1 for the easy swaps, or a regular fork if you won’t go back &amp; forth from road to gravel on separate wheelsets.</p><figure id=\"attachment_260011\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-260011\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090703/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_road-complete.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090703/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-ro