rbon 2in1 fork adds another 400€, or either regular fixed axle carbon fork for 250€.</p><figure id=\"attachment_260008\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-260008\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite.jpg\" alt=\"8bar Mitte v3 alloy all-road bike, affordable adjustable 2in1 road and gravel bike,&nbsp;riding\" width=\"1000\" height=\"570\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite-297x169.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite-800x456.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite-768x438.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26090645/8bar-Mitte-v3-alloy-all-road-bike_affordable-adjustable-2in1-all-road-gravel-bike_composite-696x397.jpg 696w,ht